I’m thrilled to see that the #FrontStreetWalls vision is being revived and is now accepting artist submissions for new murals to shine in this space! 🎨 Check out @StreetsDept’s feed for more info on how to get involved.

These walls were a passion project for nearly three years during my time at @honeygrow. What started in 2016 with an April Fools @kidhazo piece transformed into a collaborative mosaic spotlighting local artists (and an international one!) that has been the backdrop of many photo shoots over the years.

Shout out to @streetsdept @muralarts @lilahevents @goldiefalafel @mikesolomonov and the CookNSolo crew for bringing the project back online. I’m excited to see the evolution!

—— 

Tons of love to the OGs who graced these walls over the years: @kidhazo @antcarver @amberellaxo @glossblack @ndastreetart @evanlovett_art @keithwarrengreiman @lemonsparklefantasy @ayecrtv @lawrenalice @mikesmith and the students of KCAPA, with help from the incomparable @bradcarney and @muralarts. 🖤
